{
  "stem": "22840.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that increased-- inflated a bit, the size of the population, I think.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was large enough for me to think it's a large congregation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were lots of people there on Shabbat evening and-- and holidays.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And for me, it was the whole city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I know that-- that children ran around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was a large, large gathering, for a small child.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Status quo onto the Neolog yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was in the status quo ante, but he-- he was on the Orthodox side of the status quo ante.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was Orthodox side of the Neolog.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the book that was written about him, his struggle to orthodoxize, so to speak, to make more conservative the Neolog movement, are very evident.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was the 'Conservadox' type of thing in American terms, if you want.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sure there were, but I was not aware of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At the time I was not aware of any dichotomy, or any tension in Judaism.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later on, it became apparent to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think she was born in Nove Mesto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was three years younger than I am.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were ascertained from the dates of the appointment, when it was done.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, she did not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was too young at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was too young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She died very young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The maternal grandparents eventually was-- were brought to Nove Mesto to [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Eldavit. ?] So I met them frequently.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Max Berl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Her name was Hermina Berl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He died during the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She survived the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't recall exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would estimate about 10 years, because she did come to Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had the opportunity to spend time with her, in Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, in 1944.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
